 c\\u1ee9ng h\\u01a1n, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf ti\\u1ec7n d\\u1ee5ng v\\u1edbi c\\u1ed1i xay m&agrave;u trong su\\u1ed1t, t\\u1ea1o thu\\u1eadn l\\u1ee3i cho vi\\u1ec7c quan s&aacute;t th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m b&ecirc;n trong. B\\u1ea3ng \\u0111i\\u1ec1u khi\\u1ec3n v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u n&uacute;t b\\u1ea5m ri&ecirc;ng bi\\u1ec7t c\\u1ee7a t\\u1eebng ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 gi&uacute;p b\\u1ea1n d\\u1ec5 d&agrave;ng v\\u1edbi c&aacute;c thao t&aacute;c. Ngo&agrave;i ra, m&aacute;y c&oacute; quai c\\u1ea7m ch\\u1eafc ch\\u1eafn gi&uacute;p b\\u1ea1n d\\u1ec5 d&agrave;ng di chuy\\u1ec3n c\\u1ed1i; ch&acirc;n \\u0111\\u1ebf ch\\u1ed1ng tr\\u01b0\\u1ee3t \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o s\\u1ef1 an to&agrave;n v&agrave; h\\u1ea1n ch\\u1ebf r\\u01a1i v\\u1ee1 trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh xay.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>M&aacute;y xay sinh t\\u1ed1 Asanzo BL-200 v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u d\\u1ee5ng c\\u1ee5 \\u0111i k&egrave;m s\\u1ebd h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 b\\u1ea1n t\\u1ed1i \\u0111a cho c&ocirc;ng vi\\u1ec7c ch\\u1ebf bi\\u1ebfn v&agrave; s\\u01a1 ch\\u1ebf th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m. Dung t&iacute;ch c\\u1ed1i xay l\\u1edbn 1.5L gi&uacute;p xay th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nhi\\u1ec1u h\\u01a1n, c\\u1ea3 gia \\u0111&igrave;nh c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 d\\u1ec5 d&agrave;ng th\\u01b0\\u1edfng th\\u1ee9c nh\\u1eefng m&oacute;n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc u\\u1ed1ng \\u0111\\u1ea7y dinh d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng ch\\u1ec9 v\\u1edbi m\\u1ed9t l\\u1ea7n b\\u1ea5m. M&aacute;y xay sinh t\\u1ed1 Asanzo BL-200P 350W (\\u0110\\u1ecf) c&oacute; l\\u01b0\\u1ee1i dao b\\u1eb1ng inox cao c\\u1ea5p, \\u0111&ocirc;\\u0323 b&ecirc;\\u0300n cao, xay nhuy&ecirc;\\u0303n th\\u01b0\\u0323c ph&acirc;\\u0309m v\\u1edbi th\\u1eddi gian ch\\u1ec9 t&iacute;nh b\\u1eb1ng gi&acirc;y. M&aacute;y c&oacute; thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf g\\u1ecdn nh\\u1eb9, d\\u1ec5 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng v&agrave; l\\u01b0u tr\\u1eef. V\\u1edbi c&ocirc;ng su\\u1ea5t xay 350W, chi\\u1ebfc m&aacute;y xay n&agrave;y \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o xay nhuy\\u1ec5n th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m nh\\u01b0 xay sinh t\\u1ed1, xay nguy&ecirc;n li\\u1ec7u kh&ocirc;&hellip;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>M&aacute;y xay sinh t\\u1ed1 Asanzo BL-200 b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng tr\\u1ef1c tuy\\u1ebfn KingShop.vn ph&acirc;n ph\\u1ed1i ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng n&ecirc;n ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 y&ecirc;n t&acirc;m kh&ocirc;ng ph\\u1ea3i lo mua tr&uacute;ng h&agrave;ng gi\\u1ea3, h&agrave;ng nh&aacute;i, h&agrave;ng k&eacute;m ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng tr&ecirc;n th\\u1ecb tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng. Kh&ocirc;ng nh\\u1eefng v\\u1eady KingShop c\\u0169ng l&agrave; \\u0111\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng v\\u1edbi gi&aacute; c\\u1ea3 c\\u1ea1nh tranh nh\\u1ea5t th\\u1ecb tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng c&ugrave;ng v\\u1edbi \\u0111&oacute; l&agrave; ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch giao h&agrave;ng t\\u1eadn nh&agrave; trong n\\u1ed9i th&agrave;nh TP.HCM t\\u1eeb 24 &ndash; 48 gi\\u1edd t&ugrave;y theo t\\u1eebng khu v\\u1ef1c c&aacute;ch xa g\\u1ea7n tr\\u1ee5 s\\u1ee1 c\\u1ee7a c&ocirc;ng ty, kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u01b0\\u1edfng c&aacute;c ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch b\\u1ea3o h&agrave;nh theo ti&ecirc;u chu\\u1ea9n c\\u1ee7a h&atilde;ng Asanzo &aacute;p d\\u1ee5ng.<\\/p>\"}},\"category\":[\"97e1a9a7-233e-41db-8026-ded6bcebf3d7\"],\"image\":\"\\/data\\/product\\/do gia dung\\/ma\\u0301y-xay-sinh-to\\u0302\\u0301-asanzo-.jpg\",\"sku\":\"sg9\",\"alias\":\"may-xay-sinh-to-asanzo\",\"brand_id\":null,\"supplier_id\":null,\"cost\":\"1000000\",\"price\":\"1000000\",\"tax_id\":\"0\",\"stock\":\"0\",\"weight_class\":\"oz\",\"weight\":\"0\",\"length_class\":\"in\",\"length\":\"0\",\"height\":\"0\",\"width\":\"0\",\"property\":\"physical\",\"download_path\":null,\"date_available\":null,\"minimum\":\"0\",\"sort\":\"0\",\"status\":\"on\",\"approve\":\"on\",\"_token\":\"8mnFt6YVmyusjv7Wt4DGM0yWq7hsCWRFpT8wI8I8\"}', '2022-12-02 08:02:20', '2022-12-02 08:02:2