bsp;N\\u1ebfu \\u0111&atilde; n&oacute;i \\u0111\\u1ebfn vi\\u1ec7c v\\u1ec7 sinh nh&agrave; b\\u1ebfp th&igrave; ch\\u1eafc ch\\u1eafn c&ocirc;ng vi\\u1ec7c cu\\u1ed1i c&ugrave;ng trong c&ocirc;ng cu\\u1ed9c n&agrave;y \\u0111&oacute; ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; l&agrave;m s\\u1ea1ch s&agrave;n nh&agrave; b\\u1ebfp, \\u0111\\u1ec3 s&agrave;n nh&agrave; b\\u1ebfp lu&ocirc;n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1ea1ch s\\u1ebd th&igrave; ch&uacute;ng ta n&ecirc;n lau s&agrave;n nh&agrave; b\\u1ebfp m\\u1ed7i ng&agrave;y, v\\u1eeba gi&uacute;p s\\u1ea1ch s\\u1ebd l\\u1ea1i tr&aacute;nh \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c vi\\u1ec7c t&eacute; ng&atilde; do c&aacute;c lo\\u1ea1i d\\u1ea7u m\\u1ee1 trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh n\\u1ea5u \\u0103n g&acirc;y ra. \\u0110\\u1ec3 vi\\u1ec7c l&agrave;m s\\u1ea1ch s&agrave;n nh&agrave; b\\u1ebfp hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3, b\\u1ea1n c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 t&igrave;m mua c&aacute;c lo\\u1ea1i n\\u01b0\\u1edbc lau s&agrave;n s&aacute;t khu\\u1ea9n trung t&iacute;nh.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Vi\\u1ec7c&nbsp;<b>v\\u1ec7 sinh nh&agrave; b\\u1ebfp<\\/b>&nbsp;n&oacute;i chung v&agrave; c\\u1ee5 th\\u1ec3 l&agrave; l&agrave;m s\\u1ea1ch c&aacute;c b\\u1ed9 ph\\u1eadn nh\\u01b0 t\\u1ee7 l\\u1ea1nh, l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng, s&agrave;n nh&agrave; b\\u1ebfp, b\\u1ed3n r\\u1eeda b&aacute;t, ...n&oacute;i ri&ecirc;ng l&agrave; vi\\u1ec7c l&agrave;m r\\u1ea5t quan tr\\u1ecdng \\u0111\\u1ec3 gi\\u1eef cho c\\u0103n b\\u1ebfp lu&ocirc;n s\\u1ea1ch s\\u1ebd v&agrave; tho&aacute;ng m&aacute;t. &quot;Nh&agrave; s\\u1ea1ch th&igrave; m&aacute;t - b&aacute;t s\\u1ea1ch ngon c\\u01a1m&quot; m\\u1ed9t c\\u0103n b\\u1ebfp s\\u1ea1ch s\\u1ebd \\u0111em l\\u1ea1i nh\\u1eefng b\\u1eefa \\u0103n ngon cho gia \\u0111&igrave;nh cung c\\u1ea5p dinh d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng v&agrave; ng\\u0103n ng\\u1eeba b\\u1ec7nh b\\u1eb1ng nh\\u1eefng th\\u1ee9c \\u0103n t\\u1ed1t cho s\\u1ee9c kho\\u1ebb. Fact-Depot hi\\u1ec3u \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111i\\u1ec1u n&